Detected Laravel 11.x from composer.json (^11.0) and the Laravel 11+ bootstrap/app.php structure (Application::configure()).

In Laravel 11+, register middleware in bootstrap/app.php:

```php
->withMiddleware(function (Middleware $middleware) {
    $middleware->append(\App\Http\Middleware\EnsureTokenIsValid::class);
})
```

For route-specific middleware, use the `alias` method or attach in routes. This differs from Laravel 10 which used app/Http/Kernel.php.

